To implement table with fixed header along with both x axis and y axis scroll: Use Below Style  

.THIS .tableFixHead { overflow: auto; height: 550px; } 
.THIS .tableFixHead table { border-collapse: inherit; width: 100%; } 
.THIS .tableFixHead th { position: sticky; top: 0; background: white; z-index: 2; }

AND wrap you table with a Div using tableFixHead class
